item.description:
This Meetup has to do with Energy Healing, Consciousness Expansion, Psychic Development and the disclosure of previously cloistered records.

Now EVERYONE can develop capabilities once believed to be reserved only for certain "gifted" individuals.

This is the reason why technical details about Indigoes, and the role they came to play in personal and planetary healing is VERY relevant for members of this group.

Pre-ancient history is discussed, introducing the reason why Indigoes are incarnating at this time. The history discusses 3 different seedings of specific race lines here, as well as role played by various ET groups.

Technicals about the differences in Indigoes' multi-dimensional DNA energetic template are introduced, using "High Science" KS terminology (discussed at a previous Meetup).

In addition to group discussion, an informative video will be shown. A book of diagrams containing differences in the energetic template of their DNA strands will also be passed around for members to view.

The 2 hour video ends with a meditation technique. Members are welcome to bring along personal recorders, so they can repeat that technique at home later on.

If you have ANY interest in our hidden history, where we came from, and what are our evolutionary options... you can't afford to miss this Meetup!

Although these details may be new to you, the implications are PROFOUND!

This is also a WAKE-UP CALL to all who are interested in deep level energy healing...

which is MULTI-DIMENSIONAL!

It's TIME to become aware of certain VITAL truths... as necessary to partake of the immense gift the Indigoes came to bring!
